1573
01:47:47,174 --> 01:47:50,010
...there's not one shred of direct proof...

1574
01:47:50,260 --> 01:47:53,138
...that Mr. Sabich murdered Ms. Polhemus.

1575
01:47:55,682 --> 01:47:57,517
Under these circumstances...

1576
