...l cannot allow this trial to continue.

1577
01:48:01,688 --> 01:48:02,939
Mr. Sabich...

1578
01:48:04,107 --> 01:48:06,026
...you are discharged, sir.

1579
01:48:07,986 --> 01:48:11,072
